        "id": "home-hero",
        "type": "legacy-html",
        "label": "Daniel Short",
        "enabled": true,
        "variant": "default",
        "props": {
          "html": "<section class=\"hero hero--default\"><div class=\"wrapper\"><h1>Daniel Short</h1><div class=\"hero-identity\"><img class=\"hero-avatar\" src=\"img/hero/head-avatar-192.jpg\" srcset=\"img/hero/head-avatar-192.jpg 192w, img/hero/head-avatar-384.jpg 384w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 112px, 132px\" alt=\"Portrait of Daniel Short\" width=\"132\" height=\"132\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\"><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">Projects, tools, and applied data work</p></div><p class=\"hero-tagline\">This is my personal site for things I build, study, and keep refining: data projects, web tools, small games, writing utilities, and practical experiments.</p><p class=\"hero-status\">Python · SQL · JavaScript · Tableau · Machine Learning · Web Tools</p><div class=\"cta-group\"><a href=\"portfolio\" class=\"btn-primary hero-cta\">Projects</a><a href=\"tools\" class=\"btn-secondary hero-cta\">Tools</a><a href=\"games\" class=\"btn-ghost hero-cta\">Games</a></div></div><a class=\"chevron-hint scroll-indicator\" href=\"#featured-projects\" data-smooth-scroll=\"true\"><span class=\"chevron-label\">View featured work</span><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 16.5a1 1 0 0 1-.7-.29l-6-6a1 1 0 1 1 1.4-1.42L12 14.08l5.3-5.29a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 1.42l-6 6a1 1 0 0 1-.7.29z\"/></svg></a></section>"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "home-featured-projects",
        "type": "legacy-html",
        "label": "Featured Projects",
        "enabled": true,
        "variant": "default",
        "props": {
          "html": "<section id=\"featured-projects\" class=\"project-examples-band surface-band no-reveal\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"featured-projects-title\"><div class=\"wrapper\"><div class=\"project-examples-head\"><h2 id=\"featured-projects-title\">Featured Projects</h2><p class=\"project-examples-subtitle\">A few representative projects across analytics, language models, and image generation.</p></div><div class=\"project-examples-grid\" role=\"list\" aria-label=\"Featured projects\"><a class=\"project-card ripple-in project-examples-card\" role=\"listitem\" href=\"portfolio/retailStore\" aria-label=\"View Store-Level Loss and Sales ETL\"><div class=\"overlay\"></div><div class=\"project-text\"><div class=\"project-title\">Store-Level Loss &amp; Sales ETL</div><div class=\"project-subtitle\">SQL ETL and anomaly detection</div></div><picture><source srcset=\"img/projects/retailStore-640.avif 640w, img/projects/retailStore-960.avif 960w, img/projects/retailStore.avif 1410w\" type=\"image/avif\"><source srcset=\"img/projects/retailStore-640.webp 640w, img/projects/retailStore-960.webp 960w, img/projects/retailStore.webp 1410w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img src=\"img/projects/retailStore.png\" alt=\"Preview of store-level loss and sales analysis dashboard\" width=\"1410\" height=\"1410\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 92vw, 340px\"></picture></a><a class=\"project-card ripple-in project-examples-card\" role=\"listitem\" href=\"portfolio/chatbotLora\" aria-label=\"View RAG Chatbot Fine-Tuned with LoRA\"><div class=\"overlay\"></div><div class=\"project-text\"><div class=\"project-title\">RAG Chatbot Fine-Tuned with LoRA</div><div class=\"project-subtitle\">Retrieval, fine-tuning, and evaluation</div></div><picture><source srcset=\"img/projects/chatbotLora-640.avif 640w, img/projects/chatbotLora-960.avif 960w, img/projects/chatbotLora.avif 1459w\" type=\"image/avif\"><source srcset=\"img/projects/chatbotLora-640.webp 640w, img/projects/chatbotLora-960.webp 960w, img/projects/chatbotLora.webp 1459w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img src=\"img/projects/chatbotLora.png\" alt=\"Preview of chatbot architecture and interface\" width=\"1459\" height=\"914\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 92vw, 340px\"></picture></a><a class=\"project-card ripple-in project-examples-card\" role=\"listitem\" href=\"portfolio/digitGenerator\" aria-label=\"View Digit Generator\"><div class=\"overlay\"></div><div class=\"project-text\"><div class=\"project-title\">Digit Generator</div><div class=\"project-subtitle\">PyTorch generative modeling</div></div><picture><source srcset=\"img/projects/digitGenerator-640.avif 640w, img/projects/digitGenerator-960.avif 960w, img/projects/digitGenerator.avif 1410w\" type=\"image/avif\"><source srcset=\"img/projects/digitGenerator-640.webp 640w, img/projects/digitGenerator-960.webp 960w, img/projects/digitGenerator.webp 1410w\" type=\"image/webp\"><img src=\"img/projects/digitGenerator.png\" alt=\"Preview of generated handwritten digits\" width=\"1410\" height=\"1410\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 92vw, 340px\"></picture></a></div><div class=\"project-examples-actions\"><a href=\"portfolio\" class=\"btn-secondary project-examples-cta\">Browse all projects</a></div></div></section>"
        }
